## 🧠 The Debug Mindset (Remember This!)

```
Problem Reported
      ↓
kubectl get pods        ← Is it running?
      ↓
kubectl describe pod    ← What does K8s say?
      ↓
kubectl logs --previous ← What did the app say?
      ↓
kubectl get events      ← What happened in the cluster?
      ↓
Fix → Restart → Verify
```

